<h1>User Interface Design for Websites as a Visual Business Card</h1>
<p>Graphical user interfaces present your company to visitors as a centre of expertise, a contact hub and an inviting point of contact. We develop your user interface design for websites in e-commerce or for other entrepreneurial goals. With user interfaces that resonate nationally and internationally, you reach your target groups simply and efficiently.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>User Interface Design for Websites by Hob by Horse, Individually for Every Business Model</h2>
<p>Informing and controlling are the goals of every website in addition to the sales goal in the online shop or without a shop connection. Control mechanisms are not visible in the user interface design for websites, but serve as analysis tools for creating marketing campaigns and for the smooth visitor, order and payment flow.</p>

<h2>These Details Make a Customer-Friendly User Interface Design for Websites</h2>
<p>For visitors, the UI design for websites in the individual development by Hob by Horse contains the following visual and functional details:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Recognisable web design:</strong> The design development strictly follows your corporate design. Your website should be visible online in the colours and fonts of all your business materials.</li>
<li><strong>CTAs:</strong> Active websites create active visitors. You can offer demos, read-more links or free downloads. The design of all CTAs must be consistent and equally easy to use.</li>
<li><strong>User comfort:</strong> Your website probably offers further action options to your own online shop or affiliate network. Such offers should be easy to use, for example through immediate recognition of the destination when clicking on linked text elements.</li>
<li><strong>User control:</strong> Visitors like to spend comprehensive time on your website. As a reminder, offer return options or anchor links to frequently clicked menu items on the UI design.</li>
<li><strong>Understandable website language:</strong> Even as a company without an online shop, your goal is to be immediately understood by all people in your target group. We work with simple language and concise explanations of technical terms.</li>
<li><strong>Easy page access:</strong> You can offer a user interface design with high-contrast design for visually impaired people. Hearing-impaired people benefit from easy access through designs with voice support.</li>
</ul>

<h2>User Interface Design for Websites in Various Industries</h2>
<p>The fashion industry lives from the presentation of models in the online shop. On a website, you can additionally offer news from the catwalk, tips for various fashion occasions or lifestyle information. The coaching industry for start-ups and executives is also well positioned on the market.</p>

<h2>Target Group Benefits of Your Individual Web User Interface Design by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>The UI design for websites does not concern itself with the complex functional backgrounds on the user side. It must present itself competently and clearly in B2B, keep B2C customers up to date with storytelling, and convince D2C customers of the innovation of newly introduced manufacturer products.</p>
<p>Are you looking for an individual user interface design for your website or would you like to refresh the existing one with a new layout? Arrange a consultation with Hob by Horse by phone or briefly describe the UI design development goal in an email!</p>
